Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:37.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我们探寻光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}颤抖着的双手是无力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.25,0:22:44.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}呐喊又尚在远方
